### Invoice Management API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Create Invoice
POST {{baseUrl}}/invoice
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": "your-booking-uuid-here",
  "customer_id": "your-customer-uuid-here",
  "tax_amount": 5.00,
  "due_date": "2025-08-21",
  "notes": "Car wash service invoice"
}

### 2. Get All Invoices
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice

### 3. Get Invoices for Specific Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice?customerId=your-customer-uuid-here

### 4. Get Invoice Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice/stats

### 5. Get Overdue Invoices
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice/overdue

### 6. Update Overdue Invoice Statuses
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/invoice/overdue/update

### 7. Get Invoice by Invoice Number
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice/number/INV-202507-0001

### 8. Get Invoice by Booking ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice/booking/your-booking-uuid-here

### 9. Get Invoice by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/invoice/your-invoice-uuid-here

### 10. Update Invoice
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/invoice/your-invoice-uuid-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tax_amount": 7.50,
  "notes": "Updated invoice with additional tax"
}

### 11. Mark Invoice as Sent (sends email to customer)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/invoice/your-invoice-uuid-here/send

### 12. Mark Invoice as Paid
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/invoice/your-invoice-uuid-here/paid
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": "your-payment-uuid-here"
}

### 13. Delete Invoice
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/invoice/your-invoice-uuid-here
